00:05:50.440 --> 00:05:52.570
who were living in Siberia.

00:05:52.570 --> 00:05:55.130
All of them don't exist anymore.

00:05:55.130 --> 00:05:58.150
Human beings, Homo sapiens
conquered everything,

00:05:58.150 --> 00:05:59.550
rule the world.

