should include into the list--

00:09:41.050 --> 00:09:42.790
its money.

00:09:42.790 --> 00:09:45.610
Because money actually
created interaction

00:09:45.610 --> 00:09:47.220
between all human beings.

00:09:47.220 --> 00:09:49.240
Continuous interaction.

00:09:49.240 --> 00:09:53.740
It's also a sort of myth
