these three inventions.

00:39:02.390 --> 00:39:05.610
It's computer, it's internet,
and it's social networks.

00:39:05.610 --> 00:39:09.660
The one thing I can say,
that I separate all of them

00:39:09.660 --> 00:39:12.100
because I don't think
that they are free.

00:39:12.100 --> 00:39:15.420
They are dependent, but
they are still separate.

00:39:15.420 --> 00:39:17.160
Because computer
is something that

00:39:17.160 --> 00:39:21.090
makes us powerful in counting.

00:39:21.090 --> 00:39:28.920
