00:39:28.920 --> 00:39:33.890
Internet is something
that changes our--

00:39:33.890 --> 00:39:36.810
it's something like writing.

00:39:36.810 --> 00:39:42.300
When writing was created,
the information we had before

00:39:42.300 --> 00:39:44.295
