started using information

00:39:44.295 --> 00:39:45.450
in a different way.

00:39:45.450 --> 00:39:49.560
Internet-- it's the
other revolution.

00:39:49.560 --> 00:39:53.490
I know that now all of you
are thinking about today's

00:39:53.490 --> 00:39:54.750
