absolutely not necessary.

00:40:09.710 --> 00:40:11.910
We need to change everything.

00:40:11.910 --> 00:40:15.240
And countries like
Canada, like Ireland I

00:40:15.240 --> 00:40:18.360
know, Finland, South
Korea, Israel--

00:40:18.360 --> 00:40:21.690
already has changed a lot
of education of children.

00:40:21.690 --> 00:40:23.970
We in Ukraine, for
example, in Eastern Europe,

00:40:23.970 --> 00:40:28.680
still need to come closer.

00:40:28.680 --> 00:40:33.130
And there was one
questionable invention

00:40:33.130 --> 00:40:35.740
that I don't include
