00:40:41.740 --> 00:40:43.750
But I do believe that it will.

00:40:43.750 --> 00:40:46.540
And it's probably the
question, what's next?

00:40:46.540 --> 00:40:53.350
In my point of view, it's what
I would call it neuroscience

00:40:53.350 --> 00:40:55.390
