00:41:01.180 --> 00:41:04.840
We already see some things,
but it's only the beginning.

00:41:04.840 --> 00:41:08.450
I really think that it will
be a fundamental change.

00:41:08.450 --> 00:41:13.900
Both artificial intelligence
and the way of our

00:41:13.900 --> 00:41:16.060
