00:54:02.240 --> 00:54:04.040
is it's very far.

00:54:04.040 --> 00:54:07.970
And I think the bad things
makes good things, good.

00:54:07.970 --> 00:54:12.200
Because I think
that was the country

00:54:12.200 --> 00:54:24.390
when I met more happy people
than in any other place

00:54:24.390 --> 00:54:25.900
in the world.

00:54:25.900 --> 00:54:31.090
Australia, is my--
let's say, it's

00:54:31.090 --> 00:54:33.670
present number one in my chart.

00:54:33.670 --> 00:54:36.610
But you know, chart
always changes.

00:54:36.610 --> 00:54:39.040
So probably Ireland
will be one day.

00:54:39.040 --> 00:54:43.510
