00:55:01.210 --> 00:55:03.790
and doing-- you know,
I can't imagine it,

00:55:03.790 --> 00:55:08.434
not only in Ukraine, but I can't
imagine it America, in the UK--

00:55:08.434 --> 00:55:10.100
You can see it only
in Ireland, I think.

00:55:10.100 --> 00:55:11.530
It's unbelievable.

00:55:11.530 --> 00:55:13.700
How people are partying.

