00:55:50.520 --> 00:55:53.270
Elzy, and second one,
what's your opinion now

00:55:53.270 --> 00:55:56.530
about Ukrainian music?

00:55:56.530 --> 00:56:05.320
SLAVA VAKARCHUK: Our
plans for Okean Elzy,

00:56:05.320 --> 00:56:08.500
I didn't intend to talk about
that in the nearest month,

00:56:08.500 --> 00:56:11.230
so we wanted to make a
proper press conference

00:56:11.230 --> 00:56:12.310
and to say something.

00:56:12.310 --> 00:56:18.740
But I will throw
some light into that.

00:56:18.740 --> 00:56:22.340
After we finish with this
tour, which is the end of June,

00:56:22.340 --> 00:56:25.406
we'll make a break and we
don't know when will be next.

00:56:25.406 --> 00:56:26.780
We don't have any
specific plans,

00:56:26.780 --> 00:56:28.160
so we really don't
know when will

00:56:28.160 --> 00:56:31.010
be next concerts, next
tours, next album.

00:56:31.010 --> 00:56:36.710
We want to recuperate and
to relax, and just to think.

00:56:36.710 --> 00:56:40.970
And I wish we come back as soon
as possible, but I don't know.

00:56:40.970 --> 00:56:43.850
It can be a year, it can
be two, it can be five.

00:56:43.850 --> 00:56:45.290
Nobody knows.

00:56:45.290 --> 00:56:50.850
So that's something where
the question is open.

00:56:50.850 --> 00:56:51.710
Ukrainian music.

00:56:51.710 --> 00:56:53.750
Ukrainian music is unbelievable.

00:56:53.750 --> 00:56:55.610
It is booming now.

00:56:55.610 --> 00:56:59.420
I think that probably it's
one of the best periods

00:56:59.420 --> 00:57:01.160
of Ukrainian music I've seen.

00:57:01.160 --> 00:57:03.500
So many great bands
and musicians.

00:57:03.500 --> 00:57:05.520
Some of them are
still underground.

00:57:05.520 --> 00:57:07.820
Some of them are known already.

00:57:07.820 --> 00:57:09.350
But it's great.

00:57:09.350 --> 00:57:12.050
I'm looking forward to
seeing the next generation

00:57:12.050 --> 00:57:15.410
of Ukrainian musicians becoming
as popular as Okean Elzy,

00:57:15.410 --> 00:57:17.039
or even bigger.

